Package tetris.pieces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ImmutablePiece
    This interface defines the required operations of immutable Tetris pieces.
    Piece
    An interface for Tetris pieces that includes more functionality than the basic rotation/movement/x/y commands.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPiece
    A set of rotations, with position and color information.
    IPiece
    A piece shaped like the letter 'I'.
    JPiece
    A piece shaped like the letter 'J'.
    LPiece
    A piece shaped like the letter 'L'.
    OPiece
    A piece shaped like the letter 'O'.
    Rotation
    A set of 4 adjacent blocks that share the same color.
    SPiece
    A piece shaped like the letter 'S'.
    TPiece
    A piece shaped like the letter 'T'.
    ZPiece
    A piece shaped like the letter 'Z'.
